  "text": "Chimeric mice were generated by injection of 1 \u00c2 10 6 Cgt +/+ or \u00ff/\u00ff mice (CD45.2) BMNCs into lethally irradiated (12 Gy, split dose) C57BL/6-CD45.1 congenic mice [CITATION_1] .",
